ee shuttle to the strip was a good feature. We took it out there, and it dropped us off across the street from Caesar's Palace. We ended up taking a taxi back, which wasn't that expensive. We also took a taxi out to one of the shopping outlets, which had some pretty good deals. There was plenty of free parking around the hotel. Overall, it was a great stay and very easy on my wallet! I would definitely return.	
