ke too long.The room was really nice, clean, and large. Our family of 4 was very comfortable.Bathrooms were very well kept.Advice: We made sure to get a room close to the elevator, because the building is in a &quot;t&quot; shape, with very long hallways. It was a really enjoyable stay!	
