ough I must say that we did go down town as we do every year and had a great time for the day, Did great at Binons and also had the best lobster tails at Robertas in the Cortez.. All in all The Orleans is now our favorite place and we will be returning every chance we get. I hope this helps in picking a Hotel/Casino to stay at	
